io.github.retrooper.packetevents.event

Interface CancellableEvent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BukkitMoveEvent, PacketReceiveEvent, PacketSendEvent, PlayerInjectEvent, PlayerUninjectEvent

    public interface CancellableEvent
    This indicates that it is possible to cancel an event, which should result in cancelling the planned action.
